Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐江 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 快要崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐江
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.29,0:00:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐江姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想相信大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻里子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋叶星的人们一直以来都支持着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 受到他们温暖的声援和笑容的鼓励 我们才能走到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使被他们讨厌 我还是想相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信那天所获赠的善意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻里子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 对这样一无是处的我也肯说喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是超级大好人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不信的话 会遭报应的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该说你积极 还是消极呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静礼貌正确地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让大家面带微笑 变得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 小楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家面带微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个大家 也包括我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:02:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及 现在也许是敌人的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也许不能沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 总有一天说不定能相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚回去 滚回去 滚回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快滚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara的光芒这么耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使被怨恨 被攻击 你也义无反顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得如此坚强了啊 凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊酱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又见面了 优子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是被先圣老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是通过Kirara
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由双晶素召集的生命体的集体无意识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召唤到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集体无意识…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果演艺在宇宙中消失的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:04:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们的内心将会完全失去光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 与双晶素共鸣的集体无意识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在不被DES魔掌所波及的时间夹缝中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将Center Nova们召集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 我们在这里歌唱着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了人的无意识深处不被深深的绝望吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持续点亮希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当这光芒消失的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们的内心就会被黑暗吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 优子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于你们在现实世界中保护了演艺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许能够回避那样的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的 就凭我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得到的 优子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:05:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就永远也不能再在啊酱身边唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想超越啊酱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成为比啊酱更闪耀的Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 其实只是想在憧憬的前田敦子身边唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前田敦子的话就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别被骗了 她们可是背叛我们的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对 别扯淡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚出秋叶星！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于我们从秋叶星的暂时撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招从而致大家的误解 我们表示万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么下去有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们回到故乡一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}滚回去 滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是没法沟通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想传达歌声 传达爱而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠边去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌我们也没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使讨厌我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也请别讨厌歌声和演艺！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚那瞬间凪沙变成啊酱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直是那么地向往
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从她们身上获得了许多的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从古至今 代表着每一个时代的艺人们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AKB0048
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不能就此在我们这一代断送
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高烧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 难道是袭名发热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是凪沙？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特设演唱会舞台的防卫线被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是凪沙的身体顶得住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 友歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我就想在这里歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才算是我的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 凪沙 一起来鼓起阵风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咪酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我的资料库中把拍摄的景象投影到会场中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子 门的另一面是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经消失的Center Nova会照亮心中的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以由我们照亮现在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13代啊酱是如此跟我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊酱说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:09:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋叶星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们喜欢秋叶星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算被埋怨 就算被憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们0048
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对在座各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小楚
